# Sprites Directory

This directory will contain pixel art sprites for the Ralph Web UI.

## Planned Sprite Assets

- ralph-idle.png - Ralph character idle state
- ralph-thinking.png - Ralph thinking/processing animation
- ralph-working.png - Ralph actively working animation
- ralph-success.png - Ralph celebration/success state
- ralph-error.png - Ralph error/confused state
- ralph-waiting.png - Ralph waiting for input state

## Sprite Guidelines

- All sprites should be 32x32 or 64x64 pixels
- Use indexed color palette matching Simpsons theme
- Export as PNG with transparency
- Name format: {character}-{state}.png
